705569f-a.title: Brooklyn: Marcy Avenue - Division Avenue
705569f-a.text:
Marcy Ave., south from its intersection with Division Ave. In the
center is the Carnegie Library; behind it the Eastern District High School.
March 1929.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
